  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The impact of Arsha Vidya program on cognitive performance was examined in elementary school
      children. The study compares the effects of arsha vidya after school routine with usual after
      school routine in healthy 8-11 year-old Indian children.

      The main objective of the study is to investigate the effect on cognitive function, behaviour
      and emotions.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
